{"tid":814443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛記葵涌曾低見1.18元穿招股價　高位累跌九成","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T05:56:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f381703a73e1c4a9eeb0921219b84c15d31a73c4","tid":814443,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1850058/org/b22c2220f55c931fd6ee8fb4c09b967d.JPG/v7swjqUBE78eWTpV7oozEgI7Z8kzUVbw_sS2fv7Etn4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1850058%2Forg%2Fb22c2220f55c931fd6ee8fb4c09b967d.JPG%2Fv7swjqUBE78eWTpV7oozEgI7Z8kzUVbw_sS2fv7Etn4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=e633095a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年3月底掛牌的毛記葵涌（1716），今早曾低見1.18元，跌幅達5.6%；最新報1.24元，跌近0.12。毛記招股價為1.2元，上市首日曾高見11.76元，以今早低位計已累跌九成。<br />\n<br />\n去年全年少賺81%<br />\n毛記上市後首份業績按年少賺81%，當中包括一筆1,620萬元的非經常性上市開支，如果撇除這筆數，公司去年其實賺2,310萬元，按年跌幅收窄至36%。收入方面，毛記全年收入為8,675萬元，微跌近9%。"},{"pid":"6794009095dd41d6c6ef62b6b5ad032f0adb6e25","tid":814443,"uid":134958,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/165622_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F165622_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=7effc360&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82302dc0f6e225d45296287f879aae456704fe56","tid":814443,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"用最高位黎計大把創仔都係咁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7e0e17c155c3a781ef2608e148eece7a871f18","tid":814443,"uid":181719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"佢地應該出返一期或者做個節目自抽"},{"pid":"1cc7c2ca83b2575bef59038bf047eedc4ac96a84","tid":814443,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c